{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_05_03",
  "title": "miho 3話 一応考えてはおきます",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスライブ当日　開場前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Day of the Christmas Live‚ before the doors open",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "別に、ただのお墓参りなんですから\nいちいち送って下さらなくても良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just a visit to the grave.\nYou didn't have to come with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 7.5000000477
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "というより、むしろ\n独りにしていただけた方が、ありがたいのですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ to be honest‚\nI'd be thankful if you leave me alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ま……まぁ、数年前に迷惑かけたこともありますし\nどのみち、午後には一緒に会場入りですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ I caused you trouble a few years ago‚ and…\nWe have to head to the venue together this afternoon anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.4209755104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "その『一緒に』という言い方\n大変不本意なので、やめていただけませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That word \"together‚\"\nI find it extremely unpleasant. Would you mind not using it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1314196382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（いつにも増して、言い方がキツいけど）\n（調子は大分戻ったってことかな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s being more blunt than usual…）\n（but I guess that means she’s feeling better.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.3237419606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……それじゃあ、行ってきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well then‚ I'll come back later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3237419606,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.3332856000006,
          "startTime": 34.0570752462
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 36.8904085796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさん、何を話してるのかなぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wonder what Miho-san is talking about…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9904112976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for the wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8267603239,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 299.99728200000675,
          "startTime": 42.1267576059
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.2934269906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お疲れ様です……もういいんですか？\n会場入りまで、まだ少し時間はありますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ welcome back… You’re done already?\nWe still have some time before we head to the venue…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 50.6923353832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ええ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6923353832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……話したいことは、まだまだ沢山ありますけど\n続きはまた、今度来た時にします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…There’s still a lot I want to talk about‚\nbut I’ll continue next time I come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3256659985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 57.7590040844
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "万が一、本番に遅刻でもしたら\nそれこそ葉ちゃんに顔向け出来ませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I happen to be late for the performance‚\nI won't be able to face You-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1589993318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0590040844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 65.0021784624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（結局、葉さんに会うのに必要なのは）\n（ちょっとした理由……あるいは言い訳だったんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In the end‚ all she needed to see You-san was…）\n（a little reason… or excuse.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1433.3285331000097,
          "startTime": 66.4355069955
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（そのきっかけになったなら、昔の俺のミスも）\n（役に立った……ということに、しておこう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If my past mistake gave her that opportunity…）\n（then I guess it was useful… in a way.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 80.1963519096
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 80.4930235386
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 80.4930235386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、クリスマス特別ライブに来ていただいて\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you all for coming to the\nChristmas special live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2130185763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 86.046363783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "なになに、私への質問は……\nクリスマスの嬉しかった思い出、ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see‚ the question for me is…\nWhat is your happy Christmas memory?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0130185763,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 999.9881266000017,
          "startTime": 87.0463519096
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 93.546363783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "デビューしてからは、大抵クリスマスも仕事なので\nお仕事をいただけるのはとても嬉しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since debuting‚ I've usually worked on Christmas‚\nso I'm very happy to be given work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2130185763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（昼間の墓参りのことは、全然顔に出さないな）\n（こういうところは、さすがmihoさんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s not showing any sign of the grave visiting earlier.）\n（She’s really professional‚ as expected.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 107.5601730189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "あとは……そうそう、今日この会場に来る前に\n久しぶりに友達と会ってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next thing is… oh‚ right. Before coming to the venue today‚\nI met a friend for the first time in a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4601611455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "franとkanaのことじゃないわよ\n貴方達とは、年末までずっと一緒でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not you two‚ Fran and Kana.\nWe will be together until the end of the year‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5518387637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 121.593505335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "彼女とは、しばらく会っていなかったので……\n今年のクリスマスで嬉しかったのは、それですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hadn't seen her in a while… so\nThat was the happy moment of my Christmas this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7934944789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 129.2935033005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、聴いて下さい\n今日が初公開の、ⅢXのクリスマスの新曲――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now then‚ please listen.\nThis is the first public performance of IIIX’s new Christmas song――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.060159111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 137.2601682663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
